Text: greetingsCleaning out my mailbox and I find this message from John Perschke reporting on homecoming and requesting I sent you a note Sorry to delay things have been just exquisitely busy here at work the past few months So Ill send a quick note and more when I hear back from you the email address looks suspicious so Ill verify it first Big project is just wrapping up so Ill have more spare minutes soon I hope Hope all is well with you Still in Houston
